Filesystem Hierarchy

/- (root directory)
|
|- /bin
|
|- /etc
|
|- /home
|
|- /opt
|
|- /tmp
|
|- /usr
|
|- /var
|



N/B 
Absolute path - Path to a file or directory which starts from the root
/home/mike/file1/pic.jpg
Relative path - Path to a file or directory which doesnt starts from the root
/file1/pic.jpg